{"word":"G2531 - καθώς - kathṓs - kath-oce' - According to","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καθώς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kathṓs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kath-oce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">According to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆக, போல, அதுபோல, பிரகாரமாக - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"according as, just as, even as"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G5613 - ὡς - hōs - hoce/5613\">G5613</a>; <i>just</i> (or <i>inasmuch</i>) <i>as</i>, <i>that:</i> - according to, (according, even) as, how, when.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}